\par\par \uc2 Altcoins\par \b \uc2 Ripple (XRP) is Determined to be Carbon Neutral by 2030\b0\par\par\uc2 Godfrey Benjamin \par \uc2 392 \uc2 words\par \uc2 2 October 2020\par \uc2 Blockchain.News\par \uc2 BLCRNW\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2020. Worldmoney Blockchain Management Co., Limited \par \par \uc2 Ripple Labs Inc\uc2 , the blockchain company behind the Ripple (XRP) coin has declared its intentions to eliminate all of its {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/news/bitcoin-57000-times-less-environmentally-friendly-green-crypto-xrp-ripple"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 carbon footprint}}}\uc2  by 2030 while also creating the avenue for other companies willing to do the same. In a bid to achieve this, the firm {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20200930005233/en/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 said}}}\uc2  it has partnered with the Energy Web Foundation to develop and launch the EW Zero, a new, open-source tool that will enable any blockchain to decarbonize through the purchase of renewable energy in local markets worldwide.\par \par \uc2 While the mainstream adoption of blockchain and crypto is encouraging, we must constantly evaluate how we innovate to ensure the future of global finance is sustainable, says \uc2 Brad Garlinghouse\uc2 , CEO of Ripple. As digital payments continue to evolve, we need to make long-term systemic shifts as an industry to ensure digital transformation doesn't come at the cost of our planet. We are leading this change and urging all crypto players to hold themselves accountable--monitoring their energy consumption to make greener choices.\par \par \uc2 Blockchain companies are proliferating with offices relying on one form of energy or the other to power their complex processes and thus EW Zero will help firms access reliable renewable energy sources. As the firm noted, any developer can access and leverage the tool for their respective outfits.\par \par \uc2 Ripple is committing to this conservation move with backing from such conservation organizations, including REBA and \uc2 Rocky Mountain Institute\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 "Global finance is a key driver on the path to achieving a zero-net emissions energy future industrywide," says Jules Kortenhorts, CEO of \uc2 Rocky Mountain Institute\uc2 . "Blockchain and digital assets are transformative technologies and will play a pivotal role in the future of finance. Ripple is taking the lead to ensure fintech is part of the effort to build a sustainable future that is not only transformative for banks and consumers, but also beneficial for the planet."\par \par \uc2 Ripple Plays a Vital Role in the Blockchain and Crypto Adoption\par \par \uc2 Besides the company's new push for \uc2 sustainability\uc2 , Ripple is known to play a key role in helping to drive the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/news/ripple-ceo-urges-us-regulators-to-embrace-crypto-as-country-risks-falling-behind-china-"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 adoption and integration}}}\uc2  of blockchain technology and cryptocurrencies. The company is vocal in {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/news/ripple-ceo-criticizes-india-bill-to-ban-crypto-trading"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 criticizing}}}\uc2  India's incessant crypto ban.\par \par \uc2 The company is also proactive in {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/news/ripple-expands-global-regulatory-team-and-joins-blockchain-association"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 championing inclusive}}}\uc2  cryptocurrency regulations with active involvement with the blockchain association.\par \par \uc2 Document BLCRNW0020201002ega200006\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw200\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal3000\pichgoal600
