ct that Bitcoin (BTC) has never been hacked allaying fears of insecurity in the digital currency world. The underlying aim is to see if there can be a future where regulators will see cryptocurrencies and fiat as complementary and not necessarily as a threat to one another.\par \par \uc2 The Federal Reserve Bank has been proactive in the creation of a digital currency. Federal Reserve Board Governor Lael Brainaird has {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/news/federal-reserve-digital-dollar-dlt-testing-underway-cbdc-monetary-policy-lags"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  confirmed }}}\uc2  that the \uc2 United States Federal Reserve\uc2  is currently experimenting with blockchain and DLT in pursuit of its {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/tag/central-bank-digital-currency"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  central bank digital currency }}}\uc2  (CBDC) or digital dollar. The \uc2 Boston Fed\uc2  research will serve as a complement to this bigger project.\par \par \uc2 With most United States agencies {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blockchain.news/news/the-digital-dollar-continues-to-be-pushed-by-former-cftc-chair"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  bullish }}}\uc2  on digital currencies, the North American country may be closer to achieving its futuristic goal' with respect to the integration of cryptocurrencies as noted by Jim Cunha.\par \par \uc2 Document BLCRNW0020200818eg8i00005\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw200\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal3000\pichgoal600
