t concluded that although some users in the crypto community may not prefer this new Bitcoin ABC implementation. However, S chet added that the decision has been made and the November upgrade will continue as planned.\par \par \uc2 Bitcoin Cash recent tensions another split?\par \par \uc2 Chris Pacia, the lead developer of the peer-to-peer marketplace OpenBazaar and BCH developer {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://twitter.com/ChrisPacia/status/1290396565492948992"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  tweeted  }}}\uc2  on Aug. 4 that a meeting consensus was not reached over whether to make adjustments to the network's difficulty algorithm.\par \par \uc2 A difficulty algorithm adjustment (DAA) is an algorithm that adjusts the mining difficult parameter. Bitcoin (BTC) has the adjustment of the mining difficulty parameter every 2016 blocks.\par \par \uc2 Vitalik Buterin responded to the tweet saying that Bitcoin Cash people care so much and that its algorithm is fine as is.\par \par \uc2 The Bitcoin Cash community plans for an upgrade every six months, and users are concerned about another chain split.\par \par \uc2 The crypto community has reported that there have been growing tensions over the difficulty algorithm which may lead to another Bitcoin Cash split.\par \par \uc2 Document BLCRNW0020200810eg8a0000b\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw200\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal3000\pichgoal600
