\par\par \b \uc2 NEM Ventures makes investment in timestamping solution to protect IP\b0\par\par\uc2 Nawaz Ahmed \par \uc2 787 \uc2 words\par \uc2 22 July 2020\par \uc2 Brave New Coin\par \uc2 BRACOI\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 \u169\'00\'A9 2020. Brave New Coin Limited \par \par \uc2 The venture investment arm of the NEM blockchain ecosystem, NEM Ventures, has made its first investment of 2020 with SharpShark, an intellectual property timestamping solution that protects creators\u8217\'20\'19 copyrights.\par \par \uc2 SharpShark is a blockchain-powered timestamping service that helps protect copyrights and enables the transfer of intellectual property. The company was {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://ipfs01.sharpshark.io/ipfs/QmNfLNKSNfrKm8sWQNJmcBkySrfitbLN5j1pfgMLRRmY6L/certificate.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 founded}}}\uc2  in 2018 by Sasha Ivanova, designed by Valeriia Panina, and developed by Gilbert Gonzalez. Ivanova is currently the CEO, Panina is the Product Designer, and Gonzalez is now the former CTO for the startup.\par \par \uc2 Ivanova is an IT-engineer by education who enrolled in an online remote school for editors in 2017 where she got into tech writing. Since then she has gone from a blockchain startup writer to business development and product management.\par \par \uc2 Panina holds a BA in linguistics and she previously studied at and managed a school for editors and designers, where she met Ivanova. Panina started working in the crypto industry during 2017, when she worked as a content designer at a fintech media outlet before working as a managing editor at an analytical agency.\par \par \uc2 Gonzalez acquired fintech experience in Venezuela and has worked with \uc2 Goldman Sachs\uc2 . He developed a payment system for \uc2 Goldman Sachs\uc2  and later became interested in blockchain and tokenization.\par \par \uc2 Ivanova came up with the core idea behind SharpShark idea in December 2018, which was to expand and transfer a conventional timestamping method onto the Blockchain. Panina helped to visualize it and Gonzalez developed it.\par \par \uc2 The platform is built using the NEM Symbol protocol, which attracted the attention of NEM Ventures. NEM Ventures looks for strategic investments in projects which align with the ethos of the NEM community. The firm focuses on projects which demonstrate a differentiated product, the ability to generate positive net income in the medium term, and founders who showcase the desire to move the blockchain ecosystem forward.\par \par \uc2 NEM Ventures portfolio includes; Cyclebit, a crypto exchange; IODLT, an IoT and Blockchain platform; Ample, a company that helps communities to reduce their \uc2 environmental\uc2  impact, and a range of others.\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://forum.nem.io/t/sharpshark-a-symbol-powered-timestamping-and-ip-solution-to-empower-creators/25351"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 According}}}\uc2  to the NEM Ventures press release, SharpShark\u8217\'20\'19s mission is to detect plagiarism, eliminate copyright infringement, and give makers full control over their creations. \u8220\'20\'1CUltimately, the solution creates a fair and equitable decentralized solution for protecting intellectual property,\u8221\'20\'1D states NEM Ventures.\par \par \uc2 According to the company, the platform gives academics the ability to eliminate academic misconduct and establish a priority of findings. Creatives such as photographers, artists, and designers can utilize SharpShark to prove authorship and effectively track their creations in one consolidated space.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CExisting timestamping solutions have fallen short and copyright deposits are extremely costly. SharpShark\u8217\'20\'19s digital timestamping service records artwork, aiming to protect creators\u8217\'20\'19 moral rights to their work by detecting plagiarism and copyright infringement.,\u8221\'20\'1D stated Kailin O\u8217\'20\'19Donnell, Co-Founder and General Partner at NEM Ventures. \u8220\'20\'1CWe believe that all makers should have full control over their creations, and are aligned with SharpShark\u8217\'20\'19s mission to create a fair and equitable solution for protecting intellectual property.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 SharpShark publishes the digital signature of the text and images to NEMs Symbol blockchain alongside the author details to prove authorship in compliance with GDPR policy. Symbol is a protocol upgrade of NEM\u8217\'20\'19s enterprise blockchain which is due to launch later this year.\par \par \uc2 The data published on Symbol is then stored in an immutable form on the Interplanetary File System (IFPS), which is a distributed decentralized database. According to Ivanova, storing the content both in Symbol Blockchain and IPFS allows the platform to have proof of form, proof of time stamp, and proof of immutability.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CAs long-standing members of the blockchain community, we\u8217\'20\'19ve followed the NEM project for years, and the Symbol blockchain suits perfectly for intellectual property management. Symbol has a layered architecture that enables trustlessness, and performance optimisation, which was a natural fit for our solution,\u8221\'20\'1D commented Ivanova. \u8220\'20\'1CWe\u8217\'20\'19re excited to work with the NEM Ventures team to further develop our product, with the aim of making copyright and intellectual property protection more accessible and equitable.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 To date, SharpShark has tested its solution with the journalists\u8217\'20\'19 union Cispen, and the project is currently participating in the Start-Up Chile Seed acceleration program. Start-Up Chile is a public startup accelerator created by the Chilean Government for high-potential entrepreneurs to bootstrap their startups and use Chile as a foundation.\par \par \uc2 Start-Up Chile is the leading accelerator in Latin America and is among the Top 10 accelerators globally. The Seed Acceleration program is a six-month program for companies with a functional product and early validation. The accelerator funds up to 50,000,000 Chilean Peso, which is current ~US$80,000.\par \par \uc2 Document BRACOI0020200722eg7m0005l\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw200\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal3000\pichgoal600
